improved_metadata.title: Screen Printing Highland Beat
improved_metadata.description: This song describes the daily grind of a screen printing shop run by Mike and Nick, filled with hard work and a campy, upbeat energy. They're printing sunshine shirts day and night to the rhythm of their 'squeegee dance'.
